.section 'BLKSIZE (Optimal Block Size)'
.ix 'BLKSIZE Clist'
.ix CLISTs BLKSIZE
.sp
     This clist will prompt the user for the lrecl of a data-set and
then calculate the optimum blksize for 3330, 3350 and 3380"s.
.sp
.subsection 'Syntax'
.sp
%BLKSIZE

     You will be prompted for the lrecl or blank to end.

.subsection 'Sample Output'
.sp 2
%BLKSIZE
.sp
      CLIST TO COMPUTE DEVICE INDEPENDENT BLKSIZE FOR RECFM=FB DATASETS
      ENTER LRECL OF DATASET ====>
      SELECTED LRECL = 80
        IDEAL        ACTUAL     3330        3350        3380
      BLOCKSIZE    BLOCKSIZE UTILIZATION UTILIZATION UTILIZATION
        1740         1680         90%        88%         74%
        3024         2960         90%        93%         81%
        6233         6160         94%        96%         90%
